  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> active: Create Goal\n    \n    active --> paused: Pause Goal\n    active --> cancelled: Cancel Goal (with confirmation)\n    active --> completed: Complete Goal (if progress = 100% or user confirms)\n    \n    paused --> active: Resume Goal\n    paused --> cancelled: Cancel Goal (with confirmation)\n    paused --> completed: Complete Goal (if progress = 100% or user confirms)\n    \n    completed --> [*]: Final State\n    cancelled --> [*]: Final State\n    \n    note right of active\n        Default status for new goals\n        Can update progress\n        Deadline countdown active\n    end note\n    \n    note right of paused\n        Progress preserved\n        Deadline countdown paused\n        Can resume anytime\n    end note\n    \n    note right of completed\n        Final state\n        Cannot change status\n        Can archive/unarchive\n        Data preserved\n    end note\n    \n    note right of cancelled\n        Final state\n        Cannot reactivate\n        Requires confirmation\n        Data preserved for history\n    end note\n\n",
