  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个目标管理系统的状态流转图。核心场景是：用户创建目标后，目标会进入活跃状态，之后可以暂停、完成或者取消。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "completed",
        "cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那初始状态是从哪里开始？是用户直接创建目标就进入active状态吗？还有，完成和取消之后目标还能修改吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "active",
        "completed",
        "cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，创建目标后直接进入active，这是默认状态。完成和取消都是终态，不能再改了。不过completed的目标可以归档或取消归档，cancelled的彻底不能动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "completed",
        "cancelled",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我梳理一下流转：active可以暂停到paused，也可以直接完成或取消。paused之后能恢复回active，也能走向完成或取消。这样paused的出路和active类似。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "completed",
        "cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，但有一点区别：完成目标需要条件——要么进度100%，要么用户强制确认。取消操作则需要弹窗确认，避免误操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "completed",
        "cancelled",
        "progress",
        "confirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解了，我在图上标注这些条件。另外，我打算给每个状态加注释说明关键特性，比如active是默认状态、有截止日期倒计时，paused会保留进度但暂停倒计时。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题。completed和cancelled的注释也要说明是终态，数据都会保留，但cancelled的不能重新激活，completed的可以归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "completed",
        "cancelled",
        "note",
        "final state",
        "archive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，您看看。completed和cancelled都指向终态节点，四个状态都有右侧注释。流转条件也都标清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "completed",
